{"tid":1721802,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"喂！！政府想送份大禮比班建制派啊！！","createTime":"2019-11-14T18:12:30.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-14T19:05:40.000Z","uid":304782,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"1afc64a19c1019e29e5caa0a5101bca655c44d85","tid":1721802,"uid":304782,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T18:12:30.000Z","msg":"你好，我係港大GLaw 同學，我係P牌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />第一次黎，唔識規矩，多多包涵。<br />\n我就下一步行動有幾點淺見，希望可以比大家參詳：<br />\n<br />\n呢四日各位手足都辛苦了，見到手足受傷被捕好心痛、亦好憤怒。見到好多人一副死都要返工嘅嘴臉，可能佢真係熱愛返工嘅外星人，或者佢係有顧慮無得唔返都好，前線手足已經好攰，無可能日日Carry你地被罷工。<br />\n<br />\n呢場係持久戰，想阻少少時間，<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">尤其係唔知可以點樣幫手嘅和理非</span></span></strong>，希望大家睇睇。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">政府下一步係想送份大禮比建制</span></strong></span></span>。工聯會麥美娟連日就組織所謂「抗暴自救」不斷吹風，今日又預告將會公佈詳情。<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\">政府對於呢個劇本可謂係全力配合</span></span></strong>，尤其呢幾日一邊廂扮無作為，另一邊廂政務司司長張建宗就同麥美娟係立法會<strong><span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">扯貓尾</span></span></strong>：張建宗主動話現時等於進入無政府狀態，麥美娟就順勢叫無作為嘅官員辭職。<br />\n<br />\n呢一切好大機會似係<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: violet;\">為整個建制選舉工程鋪路</span></strong></span>。依家政府係藍絲之中都民望甚低，行出街都聽到唔少師奶大叔對林鄭管治無能感到失望。如果將建制打造到可以代替政府重塑秩序，相信會拉攏翻唔少淺藍甚至淺黃的選民（姐係好想返工嗰啲）<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n下星期如果警察夾埋工聯會/建制就算清到一條路，都會大肆宣傳自己嘅功勞。到時，我地保衛大學嘅努力就會成為他們的<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">人血饅頭</span></span></strong>。<br />\n<br />\n要摧毀政府精心策劃嘅呢份大禮，希望大家<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">考慮將戰線轉移到區選</span></span></strong>，煲大林鄭管治無能以及建制派為虎作倀、空口講大話。屆時，<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">建制再派人黎演抗暴自救嘅劇本就<span style=\"color: gold;\">講唔過去</span></span></strong>，任何襲擊都會成為暴力干預選舉嘅證據。<br />\n<br />\n仲有一個禮拜就區選，過去呢幾日有家累、有顧忌出唔到黎嘅和理非，希望大家出黎幫幫手做文宣。<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">勇武幫你地擋子彈，和理非都要做一場好嘅campaign</span></strong></span>，用選票話比全世界聽香港人嘅聲音。"},{"pid":"db0a742a47b9a179b9cd045ec5a6a48811008b1f","tid":1721802,"uid":262428,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T18:16:09.000Z","msg":"區選一定要贏<br />\n寸土必爭<br />\n用最多嘅政府資源嚟支持抗爭<br />\n<br />\n全民幫手拉票<br />\n說服自己父母 等如一人多兩票<br />\n一定要贏畀國際媒體睇<br />\n我哋先係大多數!"},{"pid":"0632598a4fadb2832ced70a034ec326309987f55","tid":1721802,"uid":2419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T18:17:24.000Z","msg":"兩邊都要一齊做"},{"pid":"2255e45eec76f9f33aa16255fc790da13654fc3e","tid":1721802,"uid":36238,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T18:19:00.000Z","msg":"今個月係要靠香港人嘅理性同分析力去智勝<br />\n行錯一步棋都會畀中共反擊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1ada82c5c656d00713c93ebe515867b31f3abdd8","tid":1721802,"uid":242647,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T18:27:47.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"1a1ca0a6b0090f57d46eccbbb1d02e338a0f4aaa","tid":1721802,"uid":304782,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T18:45:48.000Z","msg":"推 <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a65b029b0333d500202c3149f1d6fb37dec05957","tid":1721802,"uid":304782,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T18:55:37.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"color: violet;\">東方日報</span></strong>將呢件事落曬力咁宣傳<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\">每隔一個鐘就出一次</span></span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 見到敵人咁嘅行動真係好不安<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />但係我地好似無咩人提過咁<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2iJHnmr.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2iJHnmr.jpg&h=acc88791&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"18fe8e4be8827f94806f631d9b486b964d7d3c14","tid":1721802,"uid":304782,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T19:05:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NHiPMRq.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNHiPMRq.jpg&h=a24dab3c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n唔知點解出唔到張圖，試多次睇下得唔得<br />\n分別喺10個鐘、9個鐘、8個鐘之前佢都出一次呢篇報導，好刻意<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n希望我炒車啦"}]}